description:
A trans activist tried to pull a fast one on DMV workers by using his passport as a form of identification, as it incorrectly labeled him as female. He bragged about this scheme on social media and has since been sent a letter from the Florida DMV, thanking him for bringing this error to their attention.

Thanks to the public statements of this individual, an error has been brought to @FLHSMV's attention that has been fixed. Florida operates on truth, and Florida driver's licenses will only reflect an individual's true sex. https://t.co/5j3tt26ky9
— Bryan Griffin (@BryanDGriffin) Ja
title: Trans Activist Thought He Got Away With Lying About Gender On Driver License, But The Florida DMV Saw His Tweet
